map <C-N> <plug>NERDTreeTabsToggle<CR>

" NerdTree Toggle
autocmd VimEnter * nmap <F3> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
autocmd VimEnter * imap <F3> <Esc>:NERDTreeToggle<CR>a

" Open NerdTree at the directory of the current file
nmap <F4> :NERDTreeFind<CR>

" Default size
